@node Overview, Invoking Zee, Top, Top
@chapter Overview

Zee is an experimental editor, hosted on SourceForge at
@uref{http://sourceforge.net/projects/zee/}.  It is free software,
licensed under the GNU GPL.

Zee is written in ISO C99 for POSIX and requires the Boehm garbage
collector (libgc), PCRE (the Perl-compatible regular expressions
library), and a terminal library (either ncurses or Allegro).

